::DarkMouse::
She looked at Scorponok.
"Commander? I.." She sighed. "Oh, Never mind commander."
She turned and walked over to the console and started fine tuning the sensor 
arays.  She wanted things to work out for Quickstrike.  He deserved a nice 
bot who cared for him.  She knew she was not the one for Quickstrike.  She 
glanced over at Scorponok.  She liked him.  She wanted him to be proud of 
her.  But something held her back.  She knew that he was above her in rank.  
He wouldn't even thinkof a lowly bot like herself. She just buried herself 
in her work and tried to forget about her nagging spark.
